  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to House",
    "asOf": "2026-05-20",
    "date": "2026-05-29T12:54:10Z",
    "text": "License to Drill Act\n\nThis bill extends through FY2037 the Bureau of Land Management\u2019s (BLM\u2019s) authority to collect oil and gas permit processing fees. For each new permit application, BLM collects a fee that is transferred to the BLM Permit Processing Improvement Fund.\u00a0(Under current law, the fees are authorized through FY2026.)"
  },
